{"tid":459406,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"礦泉水開蓋後可放幾耐？","createTime":"2017-11-05T17:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T08:23:35.000Z","uid":5375,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7e9316f96e54f4463ccfa1b6c985f815a6ceceba","tid":459406,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我買開6升裝既礦泉水係屋企，只有我自己飲。<br />\n又因為公司有水機，所以屋企既礦泉水飲得好慢，一般一星期先飲得晒。<br />\n我係倒出黎飲既，瓶口應該唔會污染到。但我上星期飲少左，今日仲飲緊上星期個桶礦泉水，聞落同飲落都無怪異。跟著我上網查下，發現一般說法係開蓋後48小時內要飲晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街了，大家點睇？照飲定點，6升裝平過一般支裝好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a089f14ecf4975b4c9ed4a2123b6cae6fd31666","tid":459406,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"邊隻"},{"pid":"ee9c9095a398efa428de11568853116a93cf19e7","tid":459406,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊隻</blockquote><br />\n求其一隻，無分別"},{"pid":"5e98c5c84d60e52b232e9aea397b991a9f8a5cdb","tid":459406,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"長期咁飲法....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74533f23ab58cdcbd87711ae97d896255c294a5e","tid":459406,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:08:07.000Z","msg":"冇異味就飲得<br />\n同埋礦泉水冇營養唔會生菌 放好耐都得"},{"pid":"9a067c57f18c4faf8d6f71105b2538bc81f3b388","tid":459406,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇異味就飲得<br />\n同埋礦泉水冇營養唔會生菌 放好耐都得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc9ce3e9c8c0a1971c4f8b8a6a1c7564df5bec0","tid":459406,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長期咁飲法....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa158bcc06801a4bb00f874a30f5a588d30db0dc","tid":459406,"uid":50306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇異味就飲得<br />\n同埋礦泉水冇營養唔會生菌 放好耐都得</blockquote><br />\n你想講蒸餾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e5a9431090f8e39e45f5584c704020ab2c0c1e","tid":459406,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇異味就飲得<br />\n同埋礦泉水冇營養唔會生菌 放好耐都得</blockquote><br />\n你想講蒸餾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正路嚟講礦物質應該都係冇營養（冇能量）<br />\n都唔會生菌"},{"pid":"82390f9564ffd71a6d2913f73b0fc78b52c9afc6","tid":459406,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇異味就飲得<br />\n同埋礦泉水冇營養唔會生菌 放好耐都得</blockquote><br />\n你想講蒸餾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正路嚟講礦物質應該都係冇營養（冇能量）<br />\n都唔會生菌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八礦泉水含菌消委會籲長者孕婦等避免飲用<br />\n15.06.2009 10:53<br />\n消委會測試市面上四十款樽裝水，包括礦泉水及蒸餾水，發現Perrier的亞硝酸鹽含量超標，每升含有0.4毫克，超出天然礦泉水標準上限的三倍。消委會表示，以一個重量六十公斤的成年人計算，每天要飲十三樽礦泉水，才會超標，正常飲用不會影響健康。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有八個天然礦泉水樣本，驗出含細菌及真菌，當中FIJI Natural Artesian Water含菌量最高，每毫升含有550個菌絡，另外還包括甘露、首選牌及evian等，當中無發現致病細菌。消委會說天然礦泉水含菌是常見，但醫學會副會長陳以誠提醒，小童、孕婦、長者及免疫力差的人，避免飲用，否則最好煲過才飲用。"},{"pid":"ee09a9a2f01bcfef7d0c4b69663f949023e50cdc","tid":459406,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"唔放得<br />\n開咗就要即刻飲哂"},{"pid":"de487bd0219fa10011d6548133b7494beba9ec0e","tid":459406,"uid":37205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T18:00:18.000Z","msg":"開咗蓋就有機會有菌嫁喇，好易contaminate"},{"pid":"99352d5325582fbd3c0c7d7084ce7ec79609dcd5","tid":459406,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1daaab656fd63487a9d999f4b84904d7576c2393","tid":459406,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇異味就飲得<br />\n同埋礦泉水冇營養唔會生菌 放好耐都得</blockquote><br />\n你想講蒸餾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正路嚟講礦物質應該都係冇營養（冇能量）<br />\n都唔會生菌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八礦泉水含菌消委會籲長者孕婦等避免飲用<br />\n15.06.2009 10:53<br />\n消委會測試市面上四十款樽裝水，包括礦泉水及蒸餾水，發現Perrier的亞硝酸鹽含量超標，每升含有0.4毫克，超出天然礦泉水標準上限的三倍。消委會表示，以一個重量六十公斤的成年人計算，每天要飲十三樽礦泉水，才會超標，正常飲用不會影響健康。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有八個天然礦泉水樣本，驗出含細菌及真菌，當中FIJI Natural Artesian Water含菌量最高，每毫升含有550個菌絡，另外還包括甘露、首選牌及evian等，當中無發現致病細菌。消委會說天然礦泉水含菌是常見，但醫學會副會長陳以誠提醒，小童、孕婦、長者及免疫力差的人，避免飲用，否則最好煲過才飲用。</blockquote><br />\n真係啱啱知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65171813bcf6f222f4cc836b2bf47179630c1eae","tid":459406,"uid":42796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:22:58.000Z","msg":"我一向左放雪櫃<br />\n大約放到一星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png